{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Defend the research device against waves of enemies in this unique tower defense game! Team up with your friends or take on the challenge solo. Defeat enemies, collect resources, and use them to purchase powerful items, upgrade your character, or power up your base. The Celestial Seekers action takes place on different planets, each with its own secrets\u2014explore them, but remember, time is limited.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>COOPERATION</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you dont like going solo, team up with your friends and beat the game together, its always better to have some backup.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2797430/extras/cooperationGif.gif?t=1734118165\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>FIGHT</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from unique characters, each with their own stats and abilities\u2014find your favorite and take down the waves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2797430/extras/FightGif.gif?t=1734118165\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>BUY ITEMS</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After each wave, visit the shop to upgrade your skills, enhance your character, or buy items to help you survive the next rounds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2797430/extras/itemsGif.gif?t=1734118165\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>EXPLORE</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Once you have time and needed items, the choice is yours\u2014explore the planet or keep fighting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2797430/extras/exploreGif.gif?t=1734118165\"